WEBVTT

00:01.401 --> 00:03.702
<i>Previously on
"once upon a time"...</i>

00:03.703 --> 00:05.137
What you have is a gift.

00:05.139 --> 00:06.939
I wanted to use my magic
to help someone for so long.

00:06.941 --> 00:10.042
You're still trying to fill the
hole in your heart I created.

00:10.044 --> 00:11.043
You can't stop me.

00:11.045 --> 00:12.111
I'm not here to stop you.

00:12.113 --> 00:13.445
I'm here to do it for you.

00:14.280 --> 00:15.614
Now you are mine.

00:17.884 --> 00:19.151
Hello, rumple.

00:19.153 --> 00:20.486
How did you get here?

00:20.488 --> 00:23.188
If you don't do what I'm asking,
the savior will die.

00:23.190 --> 00:25.190
This is the only hope
the savior has of defeating her.

00:25.192 --> 00:27.493
What happens
at the end of the book?

00:27.495 --> 00:29.328
The savior fights
the final battle.

00:29.330 --> 00:31.530
No one wants to be around
to see that.

